00:57.000 --> 01:01.000
Somebody who's not asked in the front.

01:01.000 --> 01:04.000
I'm just glad to take a moment to look through the future.

01:04.000 --> 01:09.000
It's always great and we're talking today.

01:09.000 --> 01:12.000
What if you're all opinion is coming?

